[[/div]]

[[div class="chat-bubble right-msg"]]
Haha yes. Sumon shared it.
[[span class="timestamp"]]18:11[[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="chat-bubble left-msg"]]
Why are you hiding this money from us?
[[span class="timestamp"]]18:11[[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="chat-bubble right-msg"]]
Haha 🤣🤣
[[span class="timestamp"]]18:11[[/span]]
[[/div]]

