//[The camera is bouncing up and down as the cameraman runs. It finally settles on SCP-9365, who is sitting on a bright orange e-bike and checking his phone. He has a tired facial expression and a stained hi-vis vest.]//

**Cameraman**: Yo, no way, guys! Look who it is!

//[As the cameraman speaks, one-word-at-a-time captions appear at the bottom of the video. SCP-9365 looks up.]//

**Cameraman**: Today we're checking out the Bangladeshi billionaire! Mr. Babul! Say hi to TikTok!

[[span class="subject"]]**SCP-9365**[[/span]]: I'm just making a delivery, sir. Please.

**Cameraman**: //(laughing)// Look at him. Lowkey so humble. Bro, you got a billion dollars and you're riding a bike? That's crazy. Is this like a Mr. Beast video thing you're doing? Are you giving out cash? I could use the money, man. 10k would do me right.

[[span class="subject"]]**SCP-9365**[[/span]]: I don't have $10,000, man. Please leave me alone.

**Cameraman**: Damn, one of the richest guys in the world and you're still grinding. Respect, bro. Hey, can I get a selfie?

//[A small crowd has gathered. SCP-9365 tries to leave, but has to push through several people asking him to sign their dollar bills. He cycles away and turns a corner, leaving the camera's view.]//

**Cameraman**: Damn, what a guy. Check out the rest of my videos, bros! I post something every day. Make me a billionaire like Babul!
[[/div]]

