[[div class="ring-log"]]
[[div class="ring-header"]]
[[span]]
[[span class="ring-dot"]].[[/span]] VIDEO LOG: DOOR_CAM_01
[[/span]]
[[span]]2025/04/04 | 17:42:01 [[span class="ring-battery"]].[[/span]][[/span]]
[[/div]]

[[div class="ring-content"]]
//[SCP-9365 cycles up a well-tended stone path to the door and rings the bell. The recipient, a bald man wearing a silk robe and holding a glass of an unidentified green juice, opens the door and steps out. The recipient is only seen from behind.]//

[[span class="name-babul"]]**SCP-9365:**[[/span]] Your food, sir.

[[span class="name-rich"]]**Recipient:**[[/span]] I knew it. I told my assistant that if we just keep ordering, the algorithm will provide. You don't make it easy, do you, Babul Hossain?

[[span class="name-babul"]]**SCP-9365:**[[/span]] Sorry? I don't know anything about that. The order comes to $45.50.

[[span class="name-rich"]]**Recipient:**[[/span]] Right, right. $45.50. Do you want that in cash, or shall we get to talking about Series A funding?

[[span class="name-babul"]]**SCP-9365:**[[/span]] I just need the payment from the app, sir. I have other deliveries waiting.

[[span class="name-rich"]]**Recipient:**[[/span]] I love your commitment to this bit. I'm serious, the aesthetic is perfect. It's cool to see someone like you trying to understand the working class from the inside. All great geniuses are interested in logistics, you know. That's probably what brought you here. God. You look so authentic!

[[span class="name-babul"]]**SCP-9365:**[[/span]] The money, sir?

[[span class="name-rich"]]**Recipient:**[[/span]] //(Holds up his phone.)// Here's a Venmo for five thousand bucks. Consider it a 'consultation fee' for our conversation, and take my email while you're at it. I have a lot of projects I'm sure you'd be interested in. I'm working on the next generation of brands.

[[span class="name-babul"]]**SCP-9365:**[[/span]] //(Staring at the recipient's phone.)// Are you serious?

[[span class="name-rich"]]**Recipient:**[[/span]] Oh, I'm fucking serious. We could go to the moon together, Babul!

[[span class="name-babul"]]**SCP-9365:**[[/span]] Five thousand dollars? I can't take that. I'm not who you think I am.

[[span class="name-rich"]]**Recipient:**[[/span]] Fine, let's make it ten. I want to make sure you can see I'm not playing.

[[span class="name-babul"]]**SCP-9365:**[[/span]] //(Looks down at his scuffed bike and stained vest.)// I've never even... //[He raises his posture and forces a smile.]// Yeah, you've seen through me, bro. Send the 10k to my account. If the project's interesting, we can... yeah, we'll talk.

[[span class="name-rich"]]**Recipient:**[[/span]] I knew you'd see my vision! It's people like you who keep my dreams alive, Babul, and it's dreams like ours that make this whole crazy world spin round.
[[/div]]
[[/div]]

